### Fertility-Integrated Food Mechanics

#### Nutrient Density Modulation

**Energy conversion:**

```rust
if intake > 0.0 {
    let nutrient = profile.nutrient_density;  // 0.3 + fertility * 0.7
    let energy_gain = intake * (0.5 + nutrient * 0.5);
    runtime.energy = (runtime.energy + energy_gain).min(2.0);
    runtime.food_delta += energy_gain;
}
```

**Effect:** Fertile zones (nutrient=1.0) convert food to energy at 100% efficiency; barren zones (nutrient=0.3) only 65% efficiency.

#### Fertility Reproduction Bonus

**Multiplier application:**

```rust
